'''1980年[[世界大賽|世界大賽]]'''是由代表[[美國聯盟|美聯]]的[[堪薩斯市皇家|堪薩斯市皇家]]與代表[[國家聯盟|國聯]]的[[費城費城人|費城費城人]]在世界大賽中對決。<ref name=pwnfw>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=h59RAAAAIBAJ&sjid=z20DAAAAIBAJ&pg=6388%2C3553420 |work=Pittsburgh Post-Gazette |last=Feeney |first=Charley |title=Phillies win 1st world championship |date=October 22, 1980 |page=19}}</ref><ref name=wihrtstopp>{{cite magazine |url=https://vault.si.com/vault/1980/10/27/one-heartstopper-after-another-philadelphia-returned-home-with-a-3-2-world-series-margin-over-kc-when-reliever-tug-mcgraw-fanned-jose-cardenal-to-win-the-fifth-game |magazine=Sports Illustrated |last=Fimrite |first=Ron |author-link=Ron Fimrite |title=One heartstopper after another |date=October 27, 1980 |page=24 |access-date=2021-03-20 |archive-date=2020-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104023113/https://vault.si.com/vault/1980/10/27/one-heartstopper-after-another-philadelphia-returned-home-with-a-3-2-world-series-margin-over-kc-when-reliever-tug-mcgraw-fanned-jose-cardenal-to-win-the-fifth-game }}</ref><ref name=tughrstr>{{cite news |url=https://vault.si.com/vault/1980/11/03/he-kept-tugging-away-at-the-heartstrings-the-world-series-was-good-to-the-very-last-pitch-with-which-tug-mcgraw-fanned-kcs-willie-wilson-and-then-all-philadelphia-went-bonkers |magazine=Sports Illustrated |last=Fimrite |first=Ron |author-link=Ron Fimrite |title=He kept tugging at the heartstrings |date=November 3, 1980 |page=24 |accessdate=2021-03-20 |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125041114/https://vault.si.com/vault/1980/11/03/he-kept-tugging-away-at-the-heartstrings-the-world-series-was-good-to-the-very-last-pitch-with-which-tug-mcgraw-fanned-kcs-willie-wilson-and-then-all-philadelphia-went-bonkers }}</ref>最後由費城人4勝2敗打敗皇家，拿下隊史首座世界大賽冠軍。<ref name=pwnfw/><ref name=bbflows>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=tf9XAAAAIBAJ&sjid=AfcDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6496%2C5189937 |work=The Bulletin |location=(Bend, Oregon)|agency=UPI |last=Tully |first=Mike |title=Bubbly flows for the Phils |date=October 22, 1980 |page=17}}</ref><ref name=enddrgt>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=q-9VAAAAIBAJ&sjid=8eEDAAAAIBAJ&pg=6249%2C6650346|work=Eugene Register-Guard |location=(Oregon) |agency=''(Los Angeles Times)'' |last=Newhan |first=Ross |author-link=Ross Newhan |title=Phillies end long drought, begin reign |date=October 22, 1980 |page=1C}}</ref> 三壘手[[麥克·舒密特|麥克·舒密特]]成為世界大賽MVP。<ref name=schmvp>{{cite news |url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=O94hAAAAIBAJ&sjid=HqEFAAAAIBAJ&pg=2054%2C1015182 |work=Reading Eagle |location=(Pennsylvania) |agency=Associated Press |title=Schmidt's hit earns Series MVP award |date=October 22, 1980 |page=57}}</ref>

皇家隊的Willie Wilson在系列賽中被三振12次，在只有打滿6場的世界大賽中，Wilson寫下了新紀錄。

皇家隊成為繼1969年的大都會後，第二支登上世界大賽的擴編球隊。這年的世界大賽也是大聯盟首次都在人工草皮的球場舉辦的系列賽。同時也是1920年以來首次出現兩支從未奪冠的球隊在爭奪世界大賽冠軍。

世界大賽第6場，透過電視收看比賽的觀眾人數多達5490萬人，成為了史上最多人收看的世界大賽單一比賽。<ref name=Sandomir>{{cite journal|last1=Sandomir|first1=Richard|title=Baseball World Series: Postseason Vanishing From Broadcast Networks|journal=The New York Times|date=18 October 2014|volume=CLXIV|issue=56,657|pages=D4|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2014/10/18/sports/cables-ascent-tests-baseball-fans-and-their-fingers.html|access-date=25 October 2014|archive-date=2014-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141027112826/http://www.nytimes.com/2014/10/18/sports/cables-ascent-tests-baseball-fans-and-their-fingers.html}}</ref>

